  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "nrVeE3oDH0tNFm9CX5stkYPKAaCrnePTkJZtrLHmoDg=",
    "originContent": "## Features",
    "translatedContent": "## 기능"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "h0cPLmSuKz8ZWNOooWRzj04BFtCelBhlMc2TXHixOU0=",
    "originContent": "- **Full Distribution Support**: Choose between **Jazzy**, **Humble**, and **Kilted** ROS2 distros.",
    "translatedContent": "- **전체 배포 지원**: **Jazzy**, **Humble**, 그리고 **Kilted** ROS2 배포판 중 선택 가능."
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "+JZ1b1g0x6PmNj3YWVyMb06MTCpTeNgw5ct3zq7j6kE=",
    "originContent": "- **GPU Acceleration**: Automatically configures `nvidia/cuda` base images and runtime capabilities if CUDA or TensorRT is selected.",
    "translatedContent": "- **GPU 가속**: CUDA 또는 TensorRT를 선택하면 `nvidia/cuda` 베이스 이미지와 런타임 기능을 자동으로 구성."
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "cfG+HmL/k1qtUzvobp0GHhfASwF/vsfDDDkEWYmLR+E=",
    "originContent": "- **User Choice**: Handles **non-root user** creation with automatic UID/GID mapping to prevent host volume permission headaches.",
    "translatedContent": "- **사용자 선택**: 호스트 볼륨 권한 문제를 방지하기 위해 자동 UID/GID 매핑과 함께 **비루트 사용자** 생성 처리."
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "4a6CwS8Av8NxXDJ0YO2JTYWFbp2OhqH9aSRXEGcJb34=",
    "originContent": "- **Comprehensive Tooling**: Toggle common ROS2 packages (Nav2, MoveIt2, SLAM Toolbox, MoveIt, Gazebo GZ, etc.) and dev tools (colcon, rosdep, Oh-My-Zsh, SSH, X11).",
    "translatedContent": "- **종합 도구**: 일반적인 ROS2 패키지(Nav2, MoveIt2, SLAM Toolbox, MoveIt, Gazebo GZ 등) 및 개발 도구(colcon, rosdep, Oh-My-Zsh, SSH, X11)를 토글 가능."
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "0IB4myGopm4IpDsIAfGtP9KktvJyoqGe/jAIPrBvcaY=",
    "originContent": "- **Complete Output**: Generates not just a `Dockerfile`, but also a matching `docker-compose.yml` and a workspace-specific `README.md` with instructions.",
    "translatedContent": "- **완벽한 출력**: `Dockerfile`뿐만 아니라 일치하는 `docker-compose.yml`과 워크스페이스 전용 `README.md`를 함께 생성."
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "S+dZDjKJTKvbfaAJC7xMzuQ1hQkPI6seXdRY0G4J28Y=",
    "originContent": "- **Web Parity**: Identical logic engine shared with the [Web UI](https://ppswaroopa.github.io/ros2-dockergen/).",
    "translatedContent": "- **웹 동등성**: [웹 UI](https://ppswaroopa.github.io/ros2-dockergen/)와 동일한 로직 엔진 공유."
  },
